End of Train devices (EOTs) transmit brake

00:02:31.860 --> 00:02:37.189
pressure information to the engineer, who
can also adjust the air brakes with the device.

00:02:37.189 --> 00:02:41.440
This is helpful for emergencies, since even
if the train breaks in two, the brakes of

